State of Oklahoma
SPEAKER:
CHAIR:
I move to amend HB4128
Of the printed Bill
Page 2 Section 1 Lines 14
Of the Engrossed Bill
By adding after the period "." the following phrase, "The Oklahoma
Department of Wildlife Conservation may, through their rulemaking
authority, prescribe a yearly total harvest limit for black bears,
however, such yearly total harvest limit shall not be set at less than
two-hundred (200) total black bears harvested per year."
AMEND TITLE TO CONFORM TO AMENDMENTS
